text.tspan: A competitive analysis has been conducted
amongst major competitors such as Bumble,
Hinge and Plenty of Fish. We compared Tinder,
including the matchmaker feature we had ideated
to solve our user insight with other dating app
services in the market.
Upon performing the analysis, it was discovered
that no other dating app service allows users to
collaborate with friends. If Tinder Matchmaker is
successful, it will be the only dating app service
that provides a blind dating service.
No other app allows users to verify their identity.
However, Plenty of Fish combats catfishing by
using filter detecting AI. It was identified in the
feature prioritisation that verifying user IDs would
have a high level of impact, and was very doable
as there are many existing services out there that
allow users to verify their details in minutes.
Tinders strengths are its number of users. As the
most downloaded dating app in the world,
Tinders competitive advantage is its customer
base. Upon conducting the SWOT analysis, a gap
in the market was uncovered, and an opportunity
for Tinder to accommodate the needs of its users.
As Tinders users are the competitive advantage,
it is crucial for Tinder to accommodate the needs
of its existing users, so that they dont get fed up,
delete our app and move to a competitors
service.
